social_posts.post_text: Happy Bday to my little bro @ryan.gofmanas ! No kid your age works harder, and I’m incredibly thankful to have you in my life. You’re going to be one heck of a crew chief one day 👍🏻

ʀᴇᴀʟʟʏ ʟᴏᴏᴋɪɴɢ ꜰᴏʀᴡᴀʀᴅ ᴛᴏ ᴛᴇᴀᴍɪɴɢ ᴜᴘ ᴡɪᴛʜ @c4energy , ᴀɴᴅ ɢᴇᴛᴛɪɴɢ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴇꜱᴛ ꜱʜᴀᴘᴇ ᴘᴏꜱꜱɪʙʟᴇ ꜰᴏʀ ᴛʜᴇ 2023 ꜱᴇᴀꜱᴏɴ! 👊

🎥  𝕸𝖆𝖉𝕸𝖊𝖉𝖎𝖆
  @gavin.bassett

✌️ out 2022. Blessed to have the opportunities I had last year, and looking forward to 2023! Got to spend New Years in Nashville with some of my best friends and I’m beyond thankful for every one of them, my family, team, mechanical bulls, the bama rocket from broadway, and so much more!
Got to see @bailey.zimmerman tear it up last night before heading to Tulsa! He badass on stage, and out rode me bad on the mechanical bull😂😂😂
Chili Bowl Day #1 ✔️

Few laps from practice day the the Chili Bowl thanks to @floracing ! Fought a loose handling car, but overall felt comfortable and had a blast. We will make some changes and hopefully unload even better for our prelim night on Wednesday.

Officially first and last at the chili bowl!😂 congrats to two of my close friends, @kevinswindell and @joswindell on their chili bowl dub! @logan_seavey , you wheeled tf out of that thing. Congrats!!! @drinkvictory @swindellspeedlab
It’s almost that time! 🔥👊
Next Week 🏁🐊

Nothin’ tastes better than Victory, right @maxmclaughlin_ ? 

#FuelYourVictory | DrinkVictory.con
Heck of a way to start the year! My team worked their tails off all winter and it showed last night. Proud of everyone and ready to go for the next 3 nights 🏁 🐊 #blessed

Well Daytona Speedweek is in the books. Got our first win of the year out of the way, ran top 5 every night, got to watch my buddy @stenhousejr win the 500,  and spend time with some of my favorite people. 

Thankful for @jpietrowicz75 , and the entire HBR team for all their hard work this off season.  And really proud of one of my best friends @jacklehner_ for coming so close winning his first SDS Race. Your time is coming brother!
I’m excited to make my NASCAR Xfinity Series debut with @frsracing_ in the No. 96 at Watkins Glen in a few months. Thanks to everyone at FRS for making this possible!

Finished 3rd at @richmondraceway ! Thanks to Gary Putnam, Bono, and the entire 77 team for all the hard work all weekend. Came from the back 3 times and were right there at the end. Thanks to @curbrecords , Mohawk Northeast Inc., Gary, and all our sponsors for the opportunity!

Sprint Cars and Big Blocks on Saturday, Golf on Sunday! 

Shot a 45 on 9 holes, 4 pars, 0 birdies, 14 thrown club attempts, a harsh word or two, and Madison got it a decent distance off the tee box.
Live look in from last night when @jacklehner_ and I were racing back to the concession stand to get the last hot dog. 🌭

Finished 8th in my Sprint Car Debut! Fell back to 20th early before I figured out how to drive this thing 😂😂 #dirt #dirtracing #sprintcar #racing 
🎥 @gavin.bassett

Hard Work = 🏆 

🎥 @gavin.bassett
Little post work adventure this afternoon with my girl and the pups!
Opening night WINNER at Brewerton Speedway! Win #2 on the year 🏆🏆

Love how my new @bellracinghq RS7 LTWT SC turned out with the Armor Security colors! I recently switched to Bell Helmets in 2023, and have been nothing but blown away. These helmets are as light as a feather. Oh ya by the way @hd_designs , you still got it brother 🎨 🔥

Back to the drawing board this week after being lapped traffic the last few nights.

🎥 @gavin.bassett

Man we have really been off lately. Luckily all these rainouts have gave us a lot of time to regroup in the shop.  @jpietrowicz75 , and the HBR boys have all the cars setup and ready to rip, and I’m mentally ready to get some more 🏆’s 🏁. I’m excited to get back on track tomorrow! 👊
Win #3 of 2023! 🏆🏁 Proud of everyone on this team. #NeverGiveUp

🚀 🔥

🎥 @gavin.bassett

Finished 14th in my World of Outlaws Sprint Car Series Debut last night after starting 23rd. Learned so much about sprint cars, and feel like I progressed a ton throughout the night. It was beyond cool to battle with the best drivers in the country, and race side by side with one of my childhood heroes. Thanks to the Cartier Family for putting me in the seat!

social_posts.post_text: Tough day yesterday. Really struggled early and went a lap down before the first stop. We threw the kitchen sink at it, and were actually really good after the pit stop. Drove up to 7th at the checkered but was scored in 11th. We will take notes and be better for Langley.

Got to witness one of my longtime best friends pitching debut for the @mets today. Beyond proud of you @justin.jarvis15 !! He’s supported me since day 1, and I’ll support him along the whole journey! 👍🏻👏
It’s almost that time 👊 FRS Racing brought me a good looking hot rod to Watkins Glen this weekend for the NASCAR Xfinity Series Race. I’m beyond excited to be back at the Glen!
NASCAR XFINITY INSPECTION ✅
We Qualified in on speed, and will start 31st in today’s NASCAR XFINITY Series race here at Watkins Glen!

Not the day we wanted yesterday by any means. Had our fair share of issues during the race, and our day ended early due to some fluid on the track sending me hard into the last turn wall. Proud of @collin__fern and his @frsracing_team . He works his tail off to get to the race track. Just wish we had some better luck.

Watkins Glen Weekend Recap with @frsracing_team !🔥 

🎶 JETSKI @parkersharpe & @charlesham 
🎥 @gavin.bassett

Happy Birthday to my Queen ! Thank you for all you do for me, being my biggest supporter, and for making me a better person every day. I love you, I love doing life with you, and I can’t wait to see what our future holds ❤️❤️

Finished 2nd in the 200 to finish off Super Dirt Week. So close to the win.. Bummed to be one spot short of $51k, but to start the morning flipping through the air and destroying my small block, 2nd feels pretty good to end the day. Thanks to all my HBR guys, Al Heinke, and all our great sponsors. Dirt week 51 is over!
